import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from "react-redux" function SinglePage() { const selector = useSelector(state => state.singleReducer) return (
{ selector.map((a, b) => (

{a.original_title}

Language: {a.original_language}
Popularity: {a.popularity}
Release date: {a.release_date}
Vote Average: {a.vote_average}
Overview: {a.overview}
)) }
) } export default SinglePage
